'''热带风暴卡洛斯'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Carlos}}）是[[2003年太平洋飓风季|2003年太平洋飓风季]]第一个曾经[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，于6月26日经墨西哥以南的[[东风波|东风波]]发展而成。气旋在逼近海岸的同时快速增强，于6月27日清晨以[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]100公里强度从[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]]上岸。风暴接下来迅速消退成残留[[低气压|低气压区]]，然后持续到6月29日再逐渐消散。

卡洛斯在墨西哥南部部分地区降下暴雨，并以[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]两地的降雨量最高，达到337毫米。气旋沿途共令三万套房屋受损，经济损失总额约为8670万[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]（2003年墨西哥比索，相当于同年的800万[[美元|美元]]）。该国至少有九人丧生，其中七人死于[[泥石流|泥石流]]，两人死于河流洪灾，此外还有两名渔夫失踪。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Carlos 2003 track.png}}
热带风暴卡洛斯源于6月14日离开非洲西海岸的[[东风波|东风波]]，向西穿越[[大西洋|大西洋]]和[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]期间，东风波没有显著发展，卫星图像上也几乎无法观测到其踪影。到了6月20日，东风波已穿越[[中美洲|中美洲]]进入东太平洋，之后在[[特万特佩克湾|特万特佩克湾]]以南催生出[[对流|对流]]区（即[[雷暴|雷暴]]区）。<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Miles B. Lawrence | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053227/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP032003_Carlos.pdf | date = 2003-08-04 | title = Tropical Storm Carlos Tropical Cyclone Report | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP032003_Carlos.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>6月24日，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始在热带天气展望中提及这片已发展出[[低气压|低气压中心]]的天气系统<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2003-06-24 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | archivedate = 2016-08-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821070259/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2003/TWOEP.200306241620 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2003/TWOEP.200306241620 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | author = Mike Tichacek | date = 2006-06-24 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2009-05-24 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDEP/2003/TWDEP.200306241601 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821070526/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDEP/2003/TWDEP.200306241601 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-08-21 }}</ref>。由于[[风切变|风切变]]少，系统继续发展，[[雨带|雨带]]和对流都在大规模的低气压中心附近<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | date = 2003-06-24 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821070739/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2003/TWOEP.200306242249 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | archivedate = 2016-08-21 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2003/TWOEP.200306242249 }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | author = Erick Blake | date = 2006-06-24 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDEP/2003/TWDEP.200306250346 | archivedate = 2016-08-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821070932/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDEP/2003/TWDEP.200306250346 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。到了6月26日清晨，这片[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]已有充分组织，美国国家飓风中心因此将位于[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]][[埃斯孔迪多港_(瓦哈卡州)|埃斯孔迪多港]]西南偏南方向约210公里海域的系统归类成[[2003年太平洋飓风季|本季]]第三{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压，同时还开始发布公告<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | date = 2003-06-26 | title = Tropical Depression Three-E Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324044616/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep032003.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep032003.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>。

成为[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]时，低气压的环流略呈长条状，气象机构预测气旋北面的[[反气旋|反气旋]]会朝西面移动，促使低气压向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向前进并保持在海洋上空，不过，美国国家飓风中心对这样的预测并不是很有把握<ref name="disc1" />。由于[[海面温度|水温]]较高，风切变不断减少，云系逐渐组织<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2003-06-26 | title = Tropical Depression Three-E Discussion Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep032003.discus.003.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160322113131/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep032003.discus.003.shtml }}</ref>，估计热带低气压于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]6月26日达到热带风暴强度，美国国家飓风中心以“卡洛斯”（{{lang|en|Carlos}}）为其命名<ref name="tcr" />。成为热带风暴后，卡洛斯在[[低压槽|低压槽]]的影响下开始蜿蜒北上逼近墨西哥海岸<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | date = 2003-06-26 | title = Tropical Storm Carlos Discussion Five | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160326175837/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep032003.discus.005.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2009-05-26 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep032003.discus.005.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-26 }}</ref>。风暴快速强化，对流中心发展出清晰的[[风眼|眼状特征]]。估计卡洛斯于6月27日清晨以[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时100公里的最高强度从埃斯孔迪多港以西约95公里处（也是[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]][[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]东南偏东方向约245公里处）[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。<ref name="tcr" />

受墨西哥上空的反气旋影响，气旋登陆后转向西北，并且很快就减弱成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。登陆仅12小时后，卫星图像上几乎就难以再观测到环流<ref>{{cite report | author = Miles Lawrence | date = 2003-06-27 | title = Tropical Depression Carlos Discussion Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160325163026/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep032003.discus.007.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep032003.discus.007.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-25 }}</ref>。6月27日晚，卡洛斯在阿卡普尔科附近退化成不含对流的残留[[低气压|低气压区]]。环流转向西南进入太平洋，到{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}6月29日凌晨0点时已完全消散。<ref name="tcr" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Carlos_2003_rainfall.png|right]]
气旋成型后，[[墨西哥政府|墨西哥政府]]向格雷罗州阿卡普尔科至米却肯州蓬塔圣特尔莫（{{lang|en|Punta San Telmo}}）发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]，只是起初警告中仍预测风暴不会上岸<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160602082645/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/pub/ep032003.public.001.shtml | deadurl = no | date = 2003-06-26 | title = Tropical Depression Three-E Public Advisory One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/pub/ep032003.public.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-06-02 }}</ref>。卡洛斯达到热带风暴标准后，气象机构准确预测风暴将会登陆，警告范围随即调整成瓦哈卡州[[萨利纳克鲁斯|萨利纳克鲁斯]]（{{lang|en|Salina Cruz}}）至格雷罗州[[锡瓦塔内霍|锡瓦塔内霍]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2003-06-26 | title = Tropical Storm Carlos Public Advisory Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160602070343/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/pub/ep032003.public.004.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/pub/ep032003.public.004.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-06-02 }}</ref>。虽然风暴是在瓦哈卡州上岸，但其雨带还对[[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]]、[[塔巴斯科州|塔巴斯科州]]、[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]]、[[普埃布拉州|普埃布拉州]]和格雷罗州构成影响。气旋登陆当天就产生暴雨，各州的24小时最高降雨量分别是瓦哈卡州里奥韦尔迪（{{lang|en|Río Verde}}）测得的254毫米和格雷罗州[[佩塔特兰|佩塔特兰]]（{{lang|en|Petatlán}}）的112毫米<ref>{{cite report | author = Servicio Meteorológico Nacional | year = 2003 | title = Tormenta Tropical "Carlos" del Océano Pacífico | accessdate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2003/pacifico/carlos/carlos.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170616/http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2003/pacifico/carlos/carlos.html | date =  }}</ref>。墨西哥全国范围的最高降雨总量达337毫米，是在格雷罗州的马克里亚（{{lang|en|Marquelia}}）和亚佐佑测得<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/carlos2003.html | title = Tropical Storm Carlos Rainfall Summary | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141219221203/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/carlos2003.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-12-19 }}</ref>。

卡洛斯在瓦哈卜州的79个[[自治区_(墨西哥)|自治区]]产生降水或引发洪灾，大部分地区之后沦为灾区，可以获得救灾基金援助<ref>{{cite web | author = Santiago Creel Miranda and María del Carmen Segura Rangel | date = 2003-07-11 | title = Declaratoria de Desastre Natural | publisher = El Secretario de Gobernación de Mexico | accessdate = 2009-05-30 | archivedate = 2005-09-10 | url = http://www.capfce.gob.mx/web/doc/FONDENViernes11deJulio2003.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050910060840/http://www.capfce.gob.mx/web/doc/FONDENViernes11deJulio2003.pdf | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。狂风暴雨共同影响，令各地供电线缆中断，电话服务大受影响，还有两条主要公路被淹<ref name="ap627">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | date = 2003-06-23 | title = Tropical Storm Carlos dissipates after causing minor damage along Mexico's southern Pacific coast | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]]}}</ref>，此后，风暴还对其他多条道路和机场道路构成大范围破坏<ref name="sunaee">{{cite web | author = SUN-AEE | date = 2003-06-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304235915/https://www.elsiglodetorreon.com.mx/noticia/37426.toca-tierra-tormenta-tropical-carlos.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | title = Toca tierra Tormenta tropical 'Carlos' | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.elsiglodetorreon.com.mx/noticia/37426.toca-tierra-tormenta-tropical-carlos.html }}</ref>。暴雨在瓦哈卡州西北部引发[[泥石流|泥石流]]，夺走七条人命。该州另有多地爆发泥石流，共有约三万套民宅受损<ref name="dpa630" />。一个镇上有150户家庭因洪灾被迫疏散到避难所<ref name="sunaee" />。格雷罗州一条河流泛滥成灾，导致两人遇难<ref name="ap627" />。有四名渔夫失踪，或被风暴卷入大海<ref name="ap627" />，墨西哥陆军在近海搜救数天，到风暴过去四天后也只救回两人<ref name="dpa630">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | date = 2003-06-30 | title = Tropical Storm Carlos kills seven in Mexico | agency = [[德新社|Deutsche Presse-Agentur]]}}</ref>。整场风暴共令约14万8000人受到影响，经济损失总额约8670万[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]（2003年墨西哥比索，相当于同年的800万美元）<ref>{{cite web | author = Sistema Nacional de Protección Civil: Centro Nacional de Prevención de Desastres | date = 2004-03 | title = Informe de la Temporada de Ciclones Tropicales del 2003 | publisher = El Secretario de Gobernación de Mexico | url = http://www.cenapred.gob.mx/es/Transparencia/FAQ/SISI/Anexo8.2/04_03_DI_RH_23032004.pdf | accessdate = 2016-08-21 | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-08-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821111219/http://www.cenapred.gob.mx/es/Transparencia/FAQ/SISI/Anexo8.2/04_03_DI_RH_23032004.pdf }}</ref>。

